!!! 5
html
  head
    title Jade Cheat Sheet v 0.1
  body(style:"font-size:12px")
    div(style:"padding:0;border:1px black double;width:90%")
      div(style:"padding:0")
        p(style:"font-size:20px")
          a(style:"text-decoration:none;color:green",href:"http://jade-lang.com")
            < JADE >
        | Jade is a high performance template engine
        | heavily influenced by
        a(style:"text-decoration:none;color:green",href:"http://haml-lang.com")
          | Haml
        | and implemented with JavaScript for Node.        
      div(style:"float:left;padding:1px;width:49%;border:solid 1px black;")
        div(style="float:left;width:100%;")
          h1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Line Endings
          | CRLF and CR are converted to LF before parsing.
        div(style="float:left;width:100%;border:1px black solid;")
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Indentation
          | Jade is indentation based, however currently only supports 2 <emphasis>space</emphasis> indent.
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Tags
          | A tag is simply a leading word:
          DL
            DT html
            DD renders to &lt;html&gt;&lt;/html&gt;
            DT div#container and #container
            DD renders to &lt;div id="container"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            DT div.user and .user
            DD renders to &lt;div class="user"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            DT p wahoo!
            DD renders to &lt;p&gt;wahoo!&lt;/p&gt;
            DT long bodies of text begin with a pipe
            DD | foo bar
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Interpolation
          | \#{var} marks interpolation of passed local variables
          br
          | Pass {locals:{name:'tj',email:'tj@vision-media.ca'}}
          | to render,
          br
          | #user \#{name } &lt;\#{email}&gt; outputs:
          br
          | &lt;div id="user"&gt;tj &lt;tj@vision-media.ca&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Doctypes
          | Use !!! followed by an optional value below:
          ul
            li 5
            li xml
            li default
            li transitional
            li strict
            li frameset
            li 1.1
            li basic
            li mobile
          | or define your own jade.doctypes.default = 'whatever';
      div(style="float:right;padding:1px;width:49%;border:solid 1px black")
        div(style="float:left;width:100%;border 1px black solid;")
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Template
          |!!! &lt;DOCTYPE&gt;<br/>
          |html
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;head<br/>
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;title Jade Cheat Sheet<br/>
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;body<br/>
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#container<br/>
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#head<br/>
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#content<br/>
