          |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#footer<br/>
          |&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;| Copyright (c) 2010
          br
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Comments
          | Single line comments look the same as JavaScript comments
          DL
            DT \/\/ a single line comment
            DD renders as &lt;!-- a single line comment--&gt;
            DT \/\/- adding a hyphen will not output to markup
            DD
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Nesting
          | Nesting is supported by indentation
          br
          | ul
          br
          | &nbsp;&nbsp;li one
          br
          | &nbsp;&nbsp;li two
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Attributes
          | Jade supports parentheses as attribute delimiters
          br
          | And either a colon or equal sign to separate pairs:
          br
          | a(href='/login', title='View login') Login
          br
          | a(href:'/login', title='View login') Login
          H1(style:"padding:0;font-size:12px;background:gray;color:white;") Boolean Attributes
          | Boolean attributes are supported and output when true
          br
          | input(type:"checkbox", checked)